msgid ""
"Run and write Klein for Ray unit, state, architecture, integration, and "
"external-service tests."
msgstr "运行和编写 Klein for Ray 单元、状态、架构、集成及外部服务测试。"

msgid "Testing"
msgstr "测试"

msgid ""
"Klein for Ray uses pytest with a `src` layout and importlib import mode. "
"Tests are classified on two independent axes: a **tier** describes the "
"dependency boundary the test crosses, while a **component** identifies the "
"subsystem that owns it."
msgstr "Klein for Ray 使用 pytest，并采用 `src` 布局和 importlib 导入模式。测试按两个相互独立的维度分类：**层级**描述测试跨越的依赖边界，**组件**标识测试所属的子系统。"

msgid "Tier"
msgstr "层级"

msgid "Location"
msgstr "位置"

msgid "Purpose"
msgstr "用途"

msgid "Command"
msgstr "命令"

msgid "Unit"
msgstr "单元"

msgid "`tests/unit`"
msgstr "`tests/unit`"

msgid "In-process behavior with dependencies replaced at their boundary"
msgstr "在依赖边界处替换依赖后的进程内行为"

msgid "`make unit`"
msgstr "`make unit`"

msgid "State"
msgstr "状态"

msgid "`tests/state`"
msgstr "`tests/state`"

msgid "Deterministic backend and checkpoint-storage contracts"
msgstr "确定性的 Backend 和检查点存储契约"

msgid "Architecture"
msgstr "架构"

msgid "`tests/architecture`"
msgstr "`tests/architecture`"

msgid "Package and test-suite invariants"
msgstr "包与测试套件不变量"

msgid "Integration"
msgstr "集成"

msgid "`tests/integration`"
msgstr "`tests/integration`"

msgid "Behavior on a managed local Ray cluster"
msgstr "在托管本地 Ray 集群上的行为"

msgid "`make integration`"
msgstr "`make integration`"

msgid "External"
msgstr "外部"

msgid "`tests/integration/external`"
msgstr "`tests/integration/external`"

msgid "Kafka, Redis, Docker, or another service"
msgstr "Kafka、Redis、Docker 或其他服务"

msgid "`make external`"
msgstr "`make external`"

msgid ""
"`make test` is intentionally the fast, deterministic pull-request loop and "
"is an alias for `make unit`. Integration modules receive an isolated, "
"managed Ray runtime through the `ray_cluster` fixture. External tests are "
"skipped unless `--run-external` is supplied."
msgstr "`make test` 有意作为快速且确定性的 Pull Request 循环，并且是 `make unit` 的别名。集成模块通过 `ray_cluster` Fixture 获得隔离且受管理的 Ray 运行时。除非提供 `--run-external`，否则外部测试会被跳过。"

msgid "CI components"
msgstr "CI 组件"

msgid ""
"Every collected test receives exactly one component marker from `tests/"
"component_suites.py`. The same markers drive local Make targets and the "
"GitHub Actions jobs, preventing the two command sets from drifting apart."
msgstr "每个收集到的测试都会从 `tests/component_suites.py` 获得恰好一个组件 Marker。同一组 Marker 同时驱动本地 Make Target 和 GitHub Actions Job，防止两组命令发生偏离。"

