msgid ""
"The pull-request workflow encodes the architectural dependency order "
"explicitly:"
msgstr "Pull Request 工作流会显式编码架构依赖顺序："

msgid ""
"State integration includes real-Ray Memory and RocksDB checkpoint "
"restoration across a parallelism change. SQL integration restores a managed "
"streaming aggregate from a durable checkpoint. Runtime integration kills a "
"live StreamTask and requires the JobManager to replace it while keeping the "
"job running."
msgstr "状态集成测试包括在真实 Ray 上跨并行度变更恢复 Memory 和 RocksDB 检查点。SQL 集成测试从持久检查点恢复托管流式聚合。Runtime 集成测试会终止运行中的 StreamTask，并要求 JobManager 在保持作业运行的同时替换它。"

msgid "Write tests"
msgstr "编写测试"

msgid ""
"Prefer plain test functions, pytest fixtures, and `pytest.mark.parametrize`."
msgstr "优先使用普通测试函数、pytest Fixture 和 `pytest.mark.parametrize`。"

msgid ""
"Put reusable doubles and assertion helpers in `tests/support`; do not import "
"helpers from another test tier."
msgstr "将可复用的 Test Double 和断言辅助函数放入 `tests/support`；不要从其他测试层级导入辅助函数。"

msgid ""
"Use `tmp_path` and `monkeypatch` for files, environment variables, and "
"global state. Do not manually restore process state in `finally` blocks."
msgstr "对文件、环境变量和全局状态使用 `tmp_path` 与 `monkeypatch`。不要在 `finally` Block 中手动恢复进程状态。"

msgid ""
"Assert complete observable results. Avoid print-only assertions and tests "
"whose only expectation is that code does not raise."
msgstr "应断言完整的可观察结果。避免只打印结果的断言，也不要编写唯一预期仅为代码不抛出异常的测试。"

msgid ""
"Replace sleeps and open-ended polling with the `eventually` fixture. Every "
"asynchronous wait must have a timeout and an actionable failure message."
msgstr "使用 `eventually` Fixture 替代 sleep 和无限期轮询。每次异步等待都必须设置超时，并提供可指导行动的失败消息。"

msgid ""
"A test that starts Ray belongs in `tests/integration`. A test that requires "
"a service or Docker also belongs in `tests/integration/external`."
msgstr "启动 Ray 的测试应放在 `tests/integration` 中。需要服务或 Docker 的测试还应放在 `tests/integration/external` 中。"

msgid ""
"Keep test data immutable in `tests/data`; create generated output under "
"`tmp_path`."
msgstr "保持 `tests/data` 中的测试数据不可变；在 `tmp_path` 下创建生成的输出。"

msgid ""
"Per-test timeouts, strict marker/config validation, strict expected "
"failures, and warnings-as-errors are enabled globally in `pyproject.toml`."
msgstr "`pyproject.toml` 中已全局启用单测试超时、严格的 Marker/配置验证、严格的预期失败，以及将警告视为错误。"

msgid ""
"Architecture tests also enforce the observability boundaries: production "
"modules use component-scoped Klein loggers, logging calls use deferred `%s` "
"formatting, stdout writes are limited to declared user-facing boundaries, "
"and connector command buffers aren't embedded in log messages."
msgstr "架构测试还会强制执行可观测性边界：生产模块使用组件作用域的 Klein Logger，日志调用使用延迟 `%s` 格式化，stdout 写入仅限于已声明的用户可见边界，并且 Connector 命令缓冲区不得嵌入日志消息。"

msgid ""
"Documentation contract tests also keep the reference synchronized with code:"
msgstr "文档契约测试还会保持参考文档与代码同步："

msgid "every top-level export is accounted for in the API reference;"
msgstr "API 参考涵盖每个顶层导出；"

msgid "every public `DataStream` member is listed;"
msgstr "列出每个公开 `DataStream` 成员；"

msgid "every declared `ConfigOption` appears in the configuration reference;"
msgstr "每个已声明的 `ConfigOption` 都出现在配置参考中；"

msgid "standalone examples compile;"
msgstr "独立示例可以编译；"

msgid ""
"CLI and checkpoint-recovery guides use the current command and option names."
msgstr "CLI 和检查点恢复指南使用当前命令与选项名称。"

msgid ""
"`tests/integration/test_documented_examples.py` executes the standalone "
"batch SQL and finite stateful-streaming examples on the managed local Ray "
"cluster. The Sphinx CI job separately treats documentation warnings as "
"errors."
msgstr "`tests/integration/test_documented_examples.py` 会在受管理的本地 Ray 集群上执行独立批处理 SQL 示例和有限有状态流处理示例。Sphinx CI Job 另行将文档警告视为错误。"
